I move to amend SB1521
Of the printed Bill
Page 2 Section 1 Lines 22-2
Of the Engrossed Bill
by deleting subparagraph d and inserting in lieu thereof the following:
"d. is primarily designed and marketed for commercial use by business
entities, including for purposes related to customer service, a business's
operation purposes, product information and discovery, managing existing
services or goods purchased from the business, scheduling, billing and
payment, productivity and analysis related to source information, internal
research, or technical assistance,"
On Page 3, Section 1, Line 18, by inserting after the words "not include"
and before the words "an app store" the following language:
", an internet service provider,"
